{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-58","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 58","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoji drugi način za povezivanje teksta elementa <code>input</code> sa samim tim elementom. Možete umetnuti taj tekst unutar elementa <code>label</code> i dodati atribut elementa <code>for</code> sa vrednošću jednaku atributu elementa <code>input</code> iz elementa <code>id</code>.</p>\n<p>Ako postoji funkcija/karakteristika <code>input</code>, kao što je prikazano ispod:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;input id=\"breakfast\" type=\"radio\" name=\"meal\" value=\"breakfast\">\n</code></pre>\n<p>Primer elementa za <code>label</code> povezan sa ovim elementom <code>input</code> je:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;label for=\"breakfast\">Breakfast&#x3C;/label>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Povežite tekst od <code>Loving</code> i padajući meni za sortiranje unutar teksta <code>Loving</code> isključivo u elementu <code>label</code>, i dodelite mu odgovarajuće svojstvo elementa <code>for</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5efc4f528d6a74d05e68af74","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-58"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\"> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\"> Loving\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[43,45],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Morate osigurati da je element za padajući meni i dalje prisutan i da niste napravili nikakve izmene unutar njega. Mora ostati onako kako je bio u originalnom kodu.</p>","testString":"const checkboxElementRegex = /\\s*<input\\s+id\\s*=\\s*\"loving\"\\s*type\\s*=\\s*\"checkbox\"\\s*>/;\nassert.match(code, checkboxElementRegex);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš izborni okvir bi trebalo da ima svojstvo atributa <code>id</code> sa vrednošću <code>loving</code>. Očekivalo se <code>--fcc-expected--</code>, ali je pronađeno <code>--fcc-actual--</code>.</p>","testString":"const checkboxElementId = document.querySelector('input[type=\"checkbox\"]')?.getAttribute('id');\nassert.strictEqual(checkboxElementId, 'loving');"},{"text":"<p>Treba da dodate novi element <code>label</code> nakon izbornog okvira. Uverite se da ima oznaku za otvaranje i oznaku za zatvaranje.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('label'), 3);\nassert.lengthOf(code.match(/<\\/label\\>/g), 3);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>label</code> treba da bude nakon vaše selektne kutije.</p>","testString":"const checkboxElement = document.querySelector('input[type=\"checkbox\"]');\nconst checkboxSiblingElement = checkboxElement?.nextElementSibling?.nodeName;\nassert.strictEqual(checkboxSiblingElement, 'LABEL');"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element za <code>label</code> treba da ima tekst od <code>Loving</code>.</p>","testString":"const checkboxElement = document.querySelector('input[type=\"checkbox\"]');\nconst checkboxSiblingElementText = checkboxElement?.nextElementSibling?.innerText;\n\nassert.strictEqual(checkboxSiblingElementText, 'Loving');"},{"text":"<p>Tekst etikete <code>Loving</code> treba da bude samo unutar tvog novog elementa <code>label</code>. Osigurajte se da ne ponavljate taj tekst izvan elementa <code>label</code>.</p>","testString":"const checkboxElement = document.querySelector('input[type=\"checkbox\"]');\nconst checkboxSiblingNode = checkboxElement?.nextSibling?.nodeValue ?? '';\nconst labelElement = checkboxElement?.nextElementSibling;\nconst labelSiblingNode = labelElement?.nextSibling?.nodeValue ?? '';\n\nassert.notInclude(checkboxSiblingNode, 'Loving');\nassert.notInclude(labelSiblingNode, 'Loving');"},{"text":"<p>Vašem elementu <code>label</code> nedostaje atribut <code>for</code>. Uverite se da postoji razmak između naziva otvarajuće oznake <code>label</code> i atributa <code>for</code>.</p>","testString":"const checkboxElement = document.querySelector('input[type=\"checkbox\"]');\nconst checkboxSiblingElementAttr = checkboxElement?.nextElementSibling?.getAttribute('for');\n\nassert.isNotNull(checkboxSiblingElementAttr);"},{"text":"<p>Vaše svojstvo od <code>label</code> trebalo bi imati atribut svojstva <code>for</code> sa vrednošću <code>loving</code>. Očekivalo se <code>--fcc-expected--</code>, ali je pronađeno <code>--fcc-actual--</code>.</p>","testString":"const checkboxElement = document.querySelector('input[type=\"checkbox\"]');\nconst checkboxSiblingElementAttr = checkboxElement?.nextElementSibling?.getAttribute('for');\n\nassert.strictEqual(checkboxSiblingElementAttr, 'loving');"},{"text":"<p>Treba da postoji razmak između vaše opcije za odabir i vašeg novog elementa/komponente <code>label</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, />\\s+<label\\s+for\\s*=\\s*('|\")loving/);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-58","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-59","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-57","id":"5efc4f528d6a74d05e68af74","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-58"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}